flowchart TD
    User([User]) --> Auth
    Auth{Auth Check} -->|valid| Gateway
    Auth -->|invalid| Login[Login Page]
    Login --> Auth

    Gateway[API Gateway] --> RateLimit
    RateLimit{Rate Limit} -->|ok| Router
    RateLimit -->|exceeded| ErrorHandler

    Router[Router] --> ServiceA[Order Service]
    Router --> ServiceB[Product Service]
    Router --> ServiceC[User Service]

    ServiceA --> Queue[(Message Queue)]
    ServiceA --> DB1[(Orders DB)]
    ServiceB --> Cache[(Redis Cache)]
    ServiceB --> DB2[(Products DB)]
    ServiceC --> DB3[(Users DB)]

    Queue --> Worker[Background Worker]
    Worker --> Notifier[Notification Service]
    Notifier --> Email[[Email]]
    Notifier --> Push[[Push]]

    Cache -->|miss| DB2
    ErrorHandler --> Logger[Logger]
    Worker --> Logger
